      <para styleclass="Heading1">Filters</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Heading2">The Filter and Display menus and toolbars</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">These toolbars are <text styleclass="VariableName" style="color:#ff0000;">below</text> the <text styleclass="Interface">graphic-area</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted">.</text></para>
    <list id="0" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="T_Menu">Filter toolbar</text> - to help you select different element types.</li>
      <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="T_Menu">Display Elements</text> - to show or hide different element types.</li>
    </list>
